Create a bash script to automate the entire workflow:

#!/bin/ 

# Fetch data
curl -X GET "https://api.example.com/data" -H "accept: application/json" -o data.json

# Process data using Python
 3 process_data.py

# Store and visualize data
 3 visualize_data.py



Make the script executable and run it:

chmod +x data_flow.sh
./data_flow.sh



